Encon explores Providence Energy alliance . Encon Systems Inc said it is exploring a possible strategic alliance with Providence Energy Corp , which is providing working capital for a new Encon exterior lighting contract . Encon said in a press release Monday that it received a letter of intent for an exterior lighting contract from a national food service distribution company which could provide it with $ 16 . 5 million in revenues . Providence , an energy services provider , established a $ 350 , 000 line of credit to supply working capital for the new contract . 
